  <brief_title>Trial of Docetaxel-Samarium in Patients With Hormone-Refractory Advanced Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Phase II Trial of Docetaxel-Samarium in Patients With Hormone-Refractory Advanced Prostate Cancer Who Achieve a Response or a Stabilization to Docetaxel-Estramustine</official_title>
