  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective phase II trial of docetaxel-samarium in patients with
      hormone-refractory advanced prostate cancer who achieve a response or a stabilization to
      docetaxel-estramustine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
